Class Skullcab

  • java.lang.Object
    • jumpingalien.model.Organism
      • jumpingalien.model.Plant
        • jumpingalien.model.Skullcab
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Ivertical
    public class Skullcab
extends Plant
implements Ivertical
    A class of skullcabs as a special kind of plants. They are not able to jump, fall or duck, but they are capable of hovering on passable and impassable terrain. They only have 3 HP. He always wanted to be a taxi driver.
